  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1932 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The framed leaflet produced by the ‘Kasina’ cinema announces the screening of ‘Dva srca, jedan otkucaj’ (the Serbo-Croatian translation of the original German film title ‘Zwei Herzen und ein Schlag’), starring Lilian Harvey and Wolf Albach-Retty.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The film was directed by Wilhelm Thiele and released in 1932. The ‘Kasina’ cinema was founded in 1911 in Belgrade.</ab>
